!}
go-to: ministry_picker

Gustav Radbruch has been appointed Justice Minister. [? if previous_justice_party != "I" : The [+ previous_justice_party +] is displeased. ?]

@claim_finance
title: Claim Finance Ministry
unavailable-subtitle: [? if finance_minister_party = "SPD" : Already controlled ?][? if shuffle_spd_variable < 15 : Not enough leverage ?]
choose-if: finance_minister_party != "SPD" and shuffle_spd_variable >= 15
on-arrival: {!
    Q.shuffle_leverage.SPD -= 15;
    Q.shuffle_spd_variable = Q.shuffle_leverage.SPD;
    Q.previous_finance_party = Q.finance_minister_party;
    Q.finance_minister_party = "SPD";
    Q.finance_minister = "Hilferding";
    
    if (Q.previous_finance_party && Q.previous_finance_party !== 'I') {
        var rel_var = Q.previous_finance_party.toLowerCase() + '_relation';
        Q[rel_var] = Math.max(0, (Q[rel_var] || 50) - 10);
    }
!}
go-to: ministry_picker

Rudolf Hilferding has been appointed Finance Minister. [? if previous_finance_party != "I" : The [+ previous_finance_party +] is very angry. ?]

